  "title": "PT Operation Admin",
  "description": "<p>At Stag Match, we're passionate about empowering individuals and organizations through high-quality training. We foster a dynamic and supportive environment focused on learning and growth.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong> We're looking for a diligent and organized <strong>Part-Time Operations Admin</strong> to support the smooth running of our daily training activities. This role is perfect for someone who is reliable, detail-oriented, and can efficiently manage administrative tasks .</p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities :</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Training Program Support:</strong></li>\n  <li>Prepare training materials (e.g., printing, collating, organizing logistic) before sessions.</li>\n  <li>Ensure training rooms are set up and tidied before and after use.</li>\n  <li>Assist with the inventory and reordering of office and training supplies.</li>\n  <li>Simple book keeping</li>\n  <li><strong>Administrative Assistance:</strong></li>\n  <li>Perform data entry for participant registrations and attendance records.</li>\n  <li>Assist with filing and maintaining accurate physical and digital records.</li>\n  <li>Handle general office upkeep to maintain a professional environment.</li>\n  <li><strong>Coordination:</strong></li>\n  <li>Liaise with trainers regarding daily logistical needs.</li>\n  <li>Help manage outgoing and incoming mail or deliveries.</li>\n  <li>Coordinating with  learner payment etc</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Qualifications &amp; Skills:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Experience:</strong> Previous administrative or office support experience is a plus.</li>\n  <li><strong>Organization:</strong> Excellent organizational skills and a keen eye for detail.</li>\n  <li><strong>Reliability:</strong> Punctual, dependable, and able to commit to a consistent daily schedule.</li>\n  <li><strong>Initiative:</strong> Proactive in completing tasks and identifying small improvements.</li>\n  <li><strong>Communication:</strong> Basic communication skills to interact with trainers and team members.</li>\n  <li><strong>Tech Proficiency:</strong> Comfortable using Microsoft Office Suite (Word, Excel).</li>\n  <li><strong>Work Ethic:</strong> A strong desire to complete tasks efficiently and accurately..</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Schedule:</strong> Monday to Friday, 5/6PM - 8/9PM , Weekends between 9am to 5pm ( 4 to 6 hours to be discussed )</p>\n<p><strong>To Apply:</strong> If you're a self-starter with a strong work ethic and enjoy contributing to a positive learning environment, please send your resume and a brief cover letter explaining your suitability for this role to [info@stagmatch.com.sg &amp; HR@Stagmatch.com.sg] with the subject line \"Application for Part-Time Operations Admin - [Your Name]\".</p>",
